snippet.title: Primos - Official Character Trailer | Ashen Knights: One Passage
snippet.description:
Play Ashen Knights: One Passage for free at https://s.team/a/2021230.

Ashen Knights: One Passage is the prologue for Ashen Knights: Foreshadow, available for PC exclusively on Steam.

Meet Primos - the living legend of Ashen Knights. Noble and merciless he hacks and slashes through endless hordes of the Abyssal spawn, aiming to completely eliminate it, and restore his motherworld.

Primos - the ambassador of hack'n'slash, the grim slayer, the Grand Sword of Rena. Download Ashen Knights: One Passage from Steam for free and destroy the Abyss as Primos. Let your fantasy go dark in an eternal fight!
